==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uːʒən|-uːʒən]]

===Etymology===
con-fusion(lat.) to put together

===Noun===
'''confusion'''

# A lack of [[clarity]] or [[order]], [[jumble]]d.
# The state of being [[confuse]]d; not understanding.
# (''computing'') The situation where data income exceeds processing speed.

